{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_03_03",
  "title": "伊吹渚",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストのライブ当日",
      "startTime": 0.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "え、琴乃ちゃん……リハに間に合わないんですか？",
      "startTime": 3.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、午前の仕事の場所がちょっと遠かったんだが\n事故渋滞に巻き込まれたみたいなんだ",
      "startTime": 12.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "本番には間に合うんですか？　琴乃ちゃん抜きの\n四人でやる……なんて言わないですよね？",
      "startTime": 19.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いや、どんなに遅れてもリハの少し後には着くはずだ",
      "startTime": 22.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "よかった……",
      "startTime": 27.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "けど……参ったな。今日のライブは撮影も入るんだ",
      "startTime": 29.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "照明やカメラワークを見るためにも……\nリハでは誰かかわりにセンターをやってもらわないと",
      "startTime": 39.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん",
      "startTime": 43.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "あの、私に……センターの代理をやらせて下さい！",
      "startTime": 45.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "渚……いいのか？\n位置が違うと勝手もかなり変わると思うけど",
      "startTime": 54.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です",
      "startTime": 57.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "この間お話ししたことを……活かせる時が\n来たかもしれないんです",
      "startTime": 63.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんのことは、私が誰よりも分かってますから",
      "startTime": 64.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……そうか、そうだな\nよし、分かった。渚、琴乃のかわりにセンターを頼む",
      "startTime": 72.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "はい！",
      "startTime": 77.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehouse",
      "startTime": 80.2052764893
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehouse",
      "startTime": 80.2052764893
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、この曲のカメラワークについて\nご相談させていただいてもいいですか？",
      "startTime": 84.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "前にライブで、琴乃ちゃんが凄く集中した時に\nとっても素敵な笑顔を見せたんです",
      "startTime": 91.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehouse",
      "startTime": 95.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "今日のセットリスト的にも\nとてもテンションが上がると思うので……",
      "startTime": 96.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehouse",
      "startTime": 100.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "その瞬間をカメラで抜いていただけると……\nきっとまたあの笑顔が見れそうだなって",
      "startTime": 100.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehouse",
      "startTime": 107.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ありがとうございます、よろしくお願いします！",
      "startTime": 107.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "凄いな、渚……あんなに細かく相談するとは\nリハーサルが楽しみになってきたな",
      "startTime": 117.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――リハーサル開始",
      "startTime": 120.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "よろしくお願いしまーす！",
      "startTime": 123.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃の分も頑張らないと、という）\n（スイッチが入った渚は力を発揮した）",
      "startTime": 129.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "ここで、琴乃ちゃんならいつもはこう動いて……",
      "startTime": 132.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "ここで……あのスマイル！",
      "startTime": 136.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "（そっか、これが琴乃ちゃんが見てる景色なんだ……）\n（みんなの期待を舞台の中心で受けるの、凄く緊張する）",
      "startTime": 146.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、センターって）\n（とっても気持ちいいんだね、琴乃ちゃん！）",
      "startTime": 155.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "（ちょっと、ずるいなって思っちゃったよ）",
      "startTime": 158.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs022.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、今のシーンがどう映ってるか\n確認してもいいですか？",
      "startTime": 167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs023.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ、いい感じで映ってます\nありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 172.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs024.m4a",
      "text": "これならきっと\n琴乃ちゃんの可愛さが際立つと思います！",
      "startTime": 175.31163029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（結局、琴乃を立てるカメラワークや照明の相談）\n（だけじゃなく周りへの気遣いも欠かさなかったな）",
      "startTime": 182.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_03_03-ngs025.m4a",
      "text": "本番もよろしくお願いします！",
